  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055740/extras/5ffb085c44a856c78686957658f7d287.avif?t=1728316225\" width=616 height=429 /></span><br><strong>You're a rogue...<br><br>With debts to pay to the underworld, you need to make a lot of coin fast! Perhaps worse, you're wanted by the King's men for desertion. Survival is your first priority, but can you thrive in the ruthless streets of Ring City? On top of this, can you discover the secret within the walls of the city... And beneath!<br><br>Play the lovable scoundrel who just wants to enjoy his short time in this dimension!</strong><br><br>The game includes the complete story of Rogue's Choice in <strong>22 chapters</strong>. No additional purchase.<br>Rogue's Choice is a <strong>STANDALONE</strong>. It takes place in the same universe as Wizard/Demon but they are not \"connected\".<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055740/extras/720e7aeefe12b5585fe7556750172e27.avif?t=1728316225\" width=616 height=240 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055740/extras/b35a887247c813c53a44b3ea62ef3725.webp?t=1728316225\" width=616 height=57 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055740/extras/0fac5ab06879a676d589cde7d1130a8d.webp?t=1728316225\" width=15 height=20 /></span>Zero learning curve. Read the story and make decisions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055740/extras/0fac5ab06879a676d589cde7d1130a8d.webp?t=1728316225\" width=15 height=20 /></span>Outcomes are determined by decisions you make.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055740/extras/0fac5ab06879a676d589cde7d1130a8d.webp?t=1728316225\" width=15 height=20 /></span>More than 570,000 words for <strong>32+ hours of gameplay</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055740/extras/0fac5ab06879a676d589cde7d1130a8d.webp?t=1728316225\" width=15 height=20 /></span>Stay alive and sane. Use your rogue's talents and gather gold!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055740/extras/0fac5ab06879a676d589cde7d1130a8d.webp?t=1728316225\" width=15 height=20 /></span>Score and rank at the end.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055740/extras/0fac5ab06879a676d589cde7d1130a8d.webp?t=1728316225\" width=15 height=20 /></span>Ambient sounds and music.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055740/extras/0fac5ab06879a676d589cde7d1130a8d.webp?t=1728316225\" width=15 height=20 /></span>Comfort options: 8 different fonts to choose from. Tweak the font size, screen luminosity and scroll speed to your needs without restarting.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055740/extras/0fac5ab06879a676d589cde7d1130a8d.webp?t=1728316225\" width=15 height=20 /></span>Auto Saves: Restart where you stopped from.<br><br>A game by Delight Games & Cold Coffee Studio.<br>Story written by Sam Landstrom.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055740/extras/5ffb085c44a856c78686957658f7d287.avif?t=1728316225\" width=616 height=429 /></span><br><strong>You're a rogue...<br><br>With debts to pay to the underworld, you need to make a lot of coin fast! Perhaps worse, you're wanted by the King's men for desertion. Survival is your first priority, but can you thrive in the ruthless streets of Ring City? On top of this, can you discover the secret within the walls of the city... And beneath!<br><br>Play the lovable scoundrel who just wants to enjoy his short time in this dimension!</strong><br><br>The game includes the complete story of Rogue's Choice in <strong>22 chapters</strong>. No additional purchase.<br>Rogue's Choice is a <strong>STANDALONE</strong>. It takes place in the same universe as Wizard/Demon but they are not \"connected\".<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055740/extras/720e7aeefe12b5585fe7556750172e27.avif?t=1728316225\" width=616 height=240 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055740/extras/b35a887247c813c53a44b3ea62ef3725.webp?t=1728316225\" width=616 height=57 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055740/extras/0fac5ab06879a676d589cde7d1130a8d.webp?t=1728316225\" width=15 height=20 /></span>Zero learning curve. Read the story and make decisions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055740/extras/0fac5ab06879a676d589cde7d1130a8d.webp?t=1728316225\" width=15 height=20 /></span>Outcomes are determined by decisions you make.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_i